00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:49.200
♪But it was nothing but more suffering♪

00:09:50.100 --> 00:09:53.980
(Pei Residence)

00:09:54.279 --> 00:09:55.319
Uncles.

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:56.840
The three-month term has passed.

00:09:57.080 --> 00:09:59.718
Under Yao's management,
the Pei family has run in order.

00:09:59.719 --> 00:10:01.119
Nothing has gone amiss.

00:10:01.199 --> 00:10:02.759
According to our agreement,

00:10:03.080 --> 00:10:05.919
Yao should now be able
to take over as family head.

00:10:05.920 --> 00:10:07.798
If any of you still have doubts,

00:10:07.799 --> 00:10:09.639
I am ready to address them.

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:14.599
If that's the case,

00:10:14.600 --> 00:10:16.000
we have no objection

00:10:16.159 --> 00:10:17.679
to Yao becoming the family head.

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:19.400
Wait a moment.

00:10:21.560 --> 00:10:24.520
Jiang Yao is not qualified
to be family head.

00:10:25.319 --> 00:10:28.599
Third Granduncle, you made
this agreement with Yao yourself.

00:10:28.719 --> 00:10:31.599
You can't go back on your word
just because someone swayed you.

00:10:31.839 --> 00:10:34.119
If Jiang Yao had shown
true responsibility,

00:10:34.279 --> 00:10:36.039
I would honor my promise.

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:37.678
But just like Pei Yujie,

00:10:37.679 --> 00:10:39.519
he colluded
with the Japanese in secret,

00:10:39.520 --> 00:10:41.480
bringing shame on the Pei family.

00:10:41.719 --> 00:10:44.399
How can he be fit to lead?

00:10:44.400 --> 00:10:46.079
Third Granduncle, don't slander me!

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:47.919
My father was indirectly
killed by the Japanese.

00:10:47.920 --> 00:10:50.200
How could I ever work with them?

00:10:55.759 --> 00:10:57.599
Here is the proof.

00:11:00.639 --> 00:11:02.638
These are the Japanese
who mixed in with the caravan.

00:11:02.639 --> 00:11:04.359
Judging by the weight of the crates,

00:11:04.679 --> 00:11:06.279
there's no way they contain tea.

00:11:07.120 --> 00:11:08.040
Jiang Yao,

00:11:08.560 --> 00:11:10.920
you're the one in charge
of the tea trade now.

00:11:11.159 --> 00:11:12.519
Without your approval,

00:11:12.600 --> 00:11:14.840
who would dare do this?

00:11:15.880 --> 00:11:16.718
We admit it.

00:11:16.719 --> 00:11:18.798
There are things inside
that aren't tea leaves.

00:11:18.799 --> 00:11:20.519
But they're just daily goods.

00:11:20.520 --> 00:11:21.718
Supplies are scarce now.

00:11:21.719 --> 00:11:23.599
We only wanted
to make a little more profit.

00:11:23.719 --> 00:11:25.718
We'd never dare do anything else.

00:11:25.719 --> 00:11:26.399
Even now,

00:11:26.400 --> 00:11:27.759
you're still denying it.

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:29.879
Wen Yuan, bring him here.

00:11:29.880 --> 00:11:30.718
Yes.

00:11:30.719 --> 00:11:31.679
Go on.

00:11:38.319 --> 00:11:39.439
Miss Pei,

00:11:39.839 --> 00:11:42.039
take a good look. Do you know this man?

00:11:42.319 --> 00:11:44.158
Why not let him tell everyone

00:11:44.159 --> 00:11:46.039
whether those crates
hold daily goods or not?

00:11:46.040 --> 00:11:48.318
Lian Xinruo, what's the meaning of this?

00:11:48.319 --> 00:11:49.678
You drag in some stranger

00:11:49.679 --> 00:11:51.239
and think you can frame us?

00:11:52.199 --> 00:11:54.199
We've already seized the final shipment.

00:11:54.279 --> 00:11:56.199
It's on its way to the Pei family now.

00:11:56.400 --> 00:11:58.600
Soon, we can inspect it together

00:11:58.759 --> 00:12:01.199
and see what's really inside.

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:05.838
Second Master! Second Master!

00:12:05.839 --> 00:12:06.959
Second Master!

00:12:07.639 --> 00:12:09.999
Forgive me. The shipment was stolen.

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:11.120
What?

00:12:28.319 --> 00:12:31.079
Second Uncle, now you have no witness,

00:12:31.080 --> 00:12:32.560
and no physical evidence.

00:12:32.679 --> 00:12:34.919
Do you still plan
to accuse us with nothing?

00:12:40.239 --> 00:12:42.359
Whether it's daily goods
or tungsten ore,

00:12:42.520 --> 00:12:44.960
the fact remains.
You colluded with the Japanese.

00:12:45.159 --> 00:12:46.679
So in any case,

00:12:46.960 --> 00:12:49.320
Jiang Yao can never be family head.

00:12:50.239 --> 00:12:52.879
What? With your condition,

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:54.758
how can you be family head?

00:12:54.759 --> 00:12:56.039
Of course he can!

00:12:56.239 --> 00:12:59.599
Everyone has seen
Yuze's character and ability.

00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:02.560
There's no one more suitable
than him to lead.

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:04.838
What do the two of you think?

00:13:04.839 --> 00:13:06.718
Impossible! He's on the verge of death.

00:13:06.719 --> 00:13:07.999
How can he be family head?

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:08.838
Jiang Yao!

00:13:08.839 --> 00:13:10.719
Yes, with Yuze's health...

00:13:10.759 --> 00:13:12.439
Who said I'm on the verge of death?

00:13:12.600 --> 00:13:14.959
Yuze has already recovered.

00:13:14.960 --> 00:13:16.360
I am willing...

00:13:18.159 --> 00:13:19.759
to take over as family head.

